---
title: Cauliflower & Smashed Avocado Tacos with Roast Tomato Salsa & Coriander
description: Time for another taco-tastic dinner! Mexican spices mingle with roasted cauliflower and onion for a veggie packed meal that's bursting with flavour. Paired with creamy smashed avo and tangy tomato salsa, this flavour fiesta will get your tastebuds dancing.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
